				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><div class="cover"><a href="https://weightlessbooks.com/format/she-said-destroy/"><img width="75" height="116" src="https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/she-said-destroy-cover-75x116.jpg" class="attachment-sm size-sm wp-post-image" alt="She Said Destroy" title="She Said Destroy" srcset="https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/she-said-destroy-cover-75x116.jpg 75w, https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/she-said-destroy-cover-200x310.jpg 200w, https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/she-said-destroy-cover-768x1189.jpg 768w, https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/she-said-destroy-cover-400x619.jpg 400w, https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/she-said-destroy-cover-140x217.jpg 140w" sizes="(max-width: 75px) 100vw, 75px" /></a><br><div class="buy_buttons"><a href="https://weightlessbooks.com/format/she-said-destroy/"><b>$6.99</b></a><br></div></div><h3><a href="https://weightlessbooks.com/format/she-said-destroy/">She Said Destroy</a> Nadia Bulkin</h3><p>A dictator craves love&#8211;and horrifying sacrifice&#8211;from his subjects; a mother raised in a decaying warren fights to reclaim her stolen daughter; a ghost haunts a luxury hotel in a bloodstained land; a new babysitter uncovers a family curse; a final girl confronts a broken-winged monster&#8230;</p>
