				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><div class="cover"><a href="https://weightlessbooks.com/authors/the-new-voices-of-fantasy/"><img width="75" height="111" src="https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/the-new-voices-of-fantasy-cover-75x111.png" class="attachment-sm size-sm wp-post-image" alt="The New Voices of Fantasy" title="The New Voices of Fantasy" srcset="https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/the-new-voices-of-fantasy-cover-75x111.png 75w, https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/the-new-voices-of-fantasy-cover.png 200w, https://weightlessbooks.com/wp-content/uploads/images/the-new-voices-of-fantasy-cover-140x207.png 140w" sizes="(max-width: 75px) 100vw, 75px" /></a><br><div class="buy_buttons"><a href="https://weightlessbooks.com/authors/the-new-voices-of-fantasy/"><b>$9.99</b></a><br></div></div><h3><a href="https://weightlessbooks.com/authors/the-new-voices-of-fantasy/">The New Voices of Fantasy</a> Peter S.  Beage et al.</h3><p>What would you do if a tornado wanted you to be its Valentine? Or if a haunted spacesuit banged on your door? When is the ideal time to turn into a tiger? Would you post a supernatural portal on Craigslist? In these nineteen stories, the enfants terribles of fantasy have entered the building—a love-starved, ambulatory skyscraper.</p>
<p><em>The New Voices of Fantasy</em> tethers some of the fastest-rising talents of the last five years. Their tales were hand-picked by the legendary Peter S. Beagle (The Last Unicorn) and genre expert Jacob Weisman (The Treasury of the Fantastic). So go ahead, join the Communist revolution of the honeybees. The new kids got your back.</p>
<p>Includes stories by Eugene Fisher, Brooke Bolander, Amal El-Mohtar, Maria Dahvana Headley, Max Gladstone, Ben Loory, Carmen Maria Machado, Usman T. Malik, Sarah Pinsker, Hannu Rajaniemi, Adam Ehrlich Sachs, Sofia Samatar, Kelly Sandoval, Chris Tarry, A. C. Wise, Alyssa Wong, JY Yang, and E. Lily Yu.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>]]></content:encoded>
