<p>Our August 2017 issue (#131) contains:</p>
<p>* Original fiction by D.A. Xiaolin Spires (&#8220;Twisted Knots&#8221;), Nin Harris (&#8220;Reversion&#8221;), Octavia Cade (&#8220;The Stone Weta&#8221;), Sunny Moraine (&#8220;In the Blind&#8221;), Chen Qiufan (&#8220;A Man Out of Fashion&#8221;).</p>
<p>* Reprints by Sandra McDonald (&#8220;Fleet&#8221;) and Kim Stanley Robinson (&#8220;Venice Drowned&#8221;).</p>
<p>* Non-fiction by Olga Kuno, an interview with Annalee Newitz, an Another Word column by Cat Rambo, and an editorial by Neil Clarke.</p>
